Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.33,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Kokoro no tobira tozasazu ni tsuyoku... tsuyoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.33,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Leaving the door to the heart open, stronger... stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brave heart and incredible deductions,\Na rhythm that jumps to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you listen well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a unique mystery that you can only find on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.31,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Watashi ga kanjiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.31,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:47.03,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Toge okimi ni no onaji You ni ataeteita no kano shirenakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:47.03,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}this disorder I've been feeling in my heart. Perhaps you felt the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:53.47,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Nani ni kokoro o itamete nani ni obieteita no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:53.47,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Without knowing what hurt, what did I fear with my heart?
