Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.57,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}We feared to face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.95,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}This love is Thrill, Shock, Suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.95,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Love is a thrill, shock, suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:14.22,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mayoi o aoi kaze ni chirasou toshite Mo kakaekirezu ni ita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:14.22,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Even when I tried to toss my confusion to the wind. I could not hold all of it,
