Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:19.05,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}ano koro no you ni sugu ni denwashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:19.05,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Wishing to be able to be like I used to,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:22.69,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}warai aetara ii no ni ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:22.69,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}and call you right away, laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:28.03,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}chika zuite kuru shifuku no toki wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:28.03,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I can hear the steps of happiness coming closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:33.20,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}itami o tomonainagara ashi oto tateru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:33.20,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}bringing pain along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:42.04,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}kangaesugite fukami ni hamaru kimi no soba ni iru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:42.04,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}You are so focused in deep thoughts you don't realize I'm right beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:50.98,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}natsu no maboroshi hitomi tojimete ichiban saishou ni kimi o omoidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:50.98,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Summer illusions I see, closing my eyes the first one I remember is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:55.29,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}dakedo kimi to ikiteyukitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:55.29,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}and it's because I want to live with you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:00.56,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}tomadoinagara demo ii tsunaida te o hanasanaide ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:00.56,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I don't mind if you hesitate, just never let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamoto-kun was planning to take\Nall the research credit for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His friend was standing in the way of his fame and fortune,\Nso he tried to get rid of him, and frame the professor for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another advertisement...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For three days only, eat and drink as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad. You're going to do this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, give that back! It'll be terrible if it ends tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I warn you about these bars already?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I promise I won't do anything stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Who does he take us for?
